00:43:34.688 --> 00:43:39.179
Was there some other
themes that they

00:43:39.179 --> 00:43:40.925
shared about what
was actually being

00:43:40.925 --> 00:43:42.173
lost in that transformation?

00:43:48.660 --> 00:43:51.220
ROSALIND: Most
generally that when

00:43:51.220 --> 00:43:57.682
