condition of human domination

00:43:57.682 --> 00:44:01.110
you lose so much.

00:44:01.110 --> 00:44:10.100
It's the sense of loss of ways
of life, ways of thinking,

00:44:10.100 --> 00:44:15.620
experiences that humans
need to make us human.

00:44:15.620 --> 00:44:18.550
And once you displace
