00:50:08.408 --> 00:50:12.660
And so again he was looking
back to that and those aspects.

00:50:12.660 --> 00:50:16.060
ROSALIND: You know more British
history than the average bear.

00:50:16.060 --> 00:50:21.310
This is all very pertinent
to Morris particularly.

00:50:21.310 --> 00:50:23.110
Similar things were
