00:50:48.210 --> 00:50:52.180
the ducks can't swim among the
branches that you've trimmed.

00:50:52.180 --> 00:50:53.420
It's not even just pollution.

00:50:53.420 --> 00:50:55.130
It's the management.

00:50:55.130 --> 00:50:56.560
Because he looks at the bush.

00:50:56.560 --> 00:50:57.550
He doesn't see a bush.

00:50:57.550 --> 00:51:00.800
He sees an agency, I mean
in the literal sense.

00:51:00.800 --> 00:51:05.720
So that's really-- It doesn't
have to be destruction.

00:51:05.720 --> 00:51:09.030
It can just be the
sense-- Well, again,

00:51:09.030 --> 00:51:11.390
one of my favorite quotes
